docs.title: Welcome to Fabreeko Docs!
docs.text:
Welcome to the official documentation hub for Fabreeko. We aim to be a place for 3D printer enthusiasts to find parts and printers in a curated selection dedicated to supporting the community. We pride ourselves on our deep knowledge of all types of 3D printers and parts, as well as our willingness to help you find exactly what you're looking for!

Work In Progress

You are reading this before the site has launched and missing work. This notification will be removed when ready.

Looking for a specific product?

Use the search bar at the top of this page or the menu to the left.

docs.title: What You'll Find Here
docs.text:
This site is designed to help makers, modders, and professionals get the most out of their Fabreeko gear. In time, you'll find:

  • Assembly guides for our DIY kits
  • Installation manuals for accessories and upgrades
  • Reference docs on firmware, tuning, and maintenance
  • Community projects and advanced mods
  • Troubleshooting tips and FAQs

docs.title: Get Started
docs.text: Ready to build or upgrade your machine? Start by browsing the menu to the left.

docs.title: Join the Community
docs.text:
Have questions or want to share your build? You're not alone. Join our active community:

  • Fabreeko Discord
  • or Contact Us

Made with ❤️ and a little bit of filament.
